State Regulations
(a) Route 204. The
eastbound and westbound roadways of Route 204 between IR 490 and Chili Avenue, Route 33A. (b) Route 33A and Route
204 (Chili Avenue) between Route 204 (Airport Expressway) and Route 204 (Brooks

Avenue). (c) Deep Rock Road between

Route 204 (Brooks Avenue) and a point 1,300+- feet south of Route 204 (Brooks

Avenue). (d) Route 33 (Buffalo

Road) between Gellwood Drive and Route 490. (e) [Repealed]
(f) Person Place. Person Place between Lee

Road and a distance of 530+- feet east of Lee Road. (g) Lee Road. Lee Road between Person Place
and Route 31 (Lyell Avenue). (h) Route 386/CR 158 (Elmgrove Road). Route 386/CR 158 (Elmgrove Road) between

Route 531 and Route 31 in the Town of Gates. Notes
